<div class="design-viz-block">
    <h3>BIM-Моделирование: Генерация Проекта</h3>
    <div class="viz-placeholder">
        
        <svg class="blueprint-svg" viewBox="0 0 500 250" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            
            <g class="draw-path">
                <path d="M 50 80 L 450 80" />
                <path d="M 120 50 L 120 110" />
                <path d="M 380 50 L 380 110" />
                <rect x="180" y="50" width="100" height="60" />
                <path d="M 220 80 L 220 40" />
                <path d="M 60 70 L 110 90" />
                <path d="M 60 90 L 110 70" />
            </g>

            <g class="draw-path draw-delay">
                <path d="M 50 180 L 450 180" />
                <path d="M 150 150 L 150 210" />
                <path d="M 400 150 L 400 210" />
                <rect x="250" y="150" width="100" height="60" />
                <path d="M 300 180 L 300 220" />
                <path d="M 400 170 L 450 190" />
                <path d="M 400 190 L 450 170" />
            </g>

            <g class="draw-path" style="animation-delay: 4.5s;">
                <path d="M 220 40 L 250 10 L 300 10 L 300 40" /> 
                <rect x="230" y="10" width="80" height="30" />
            </g>
            
        </svg>
        
        <div class="viz-status">
            >> PROJECT UUTE: **IVANOVO-01**<br>
            >> LASER TRACING: ACTIVE
        </div>
    </div>
    <p style="color:var(--text-gray); font-size:14px; margin-top:15px;">
        Создаем точную цифровую модель узла учета, исключая ошибки на этапе монтажа.
    </p>
</div>

<style>
    .design-viz-block {
        margin-top: 80px;
        padding: 40px;
        background: var(--bg-panel);
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05);
    }
    .design-viz-block h3 {
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .viz-placeholder {
        min-height: 400px;
        background-color: #050507;
        background-image: 
            linear-gradient(rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.15) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);
        background-size: 30px 30px; 
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-dim);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .blueprint-svg {
        width: 90%;
        height: auto;
        max-width: 700px;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px var(--accent)); 
    }

    .draw-path {
        stroke: var(--accent);
        stroke-width: 3;
        stroke-linecap: round;
        fill: none;
        stroke-dasharray: 2000;
        stroke-dashoffset: 2000;
        animation: laser-draw 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .draw-delay {
        animation-delay: 2.5s;
    }

    @keyframes laser-draw {
        0% { stroke-dashoffset: 2000; opacity: 0; }
        10% { opacity: 1; }
        80% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; opacity: 1; }
        90% { opacity: 1; }
        100% { stroke-dashoffset: 0; opacity: 0; }
    }

    .viz-status {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 20px;
        left: 20px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        color: var(--success);
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: left;
        z-index: 10;
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 255, 128, 0.5);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .viz-placeholder { min-height: 300px; }
    }
</style>